# Storefront Theme Customisation — Implementation Plan

> **Status: Awaiting final visual approval before execution**

## Core Constraints

| Rule | Detail |
|---|---|
| 🚫 Don't touch existing code | Existing serializers, views, `StorefrontExperience.js` stay exactly as-is |
| 🆕 New model for new data | New `StorefrontConfig` Django model. Old `Store.themes` field stays and is decommissioned later |
| 📐 Expandable theme registry | A registry file defines all themes. Adding a new one = add an entry + build a component |
| 🛍 E-commerce themes only | Product-first layouts, not editorial/blog |
| 💎 Gold + Platinum gate | `plan == 'G'` (Gold) or `plan == 'P'` (Platinum) |
| 📝 Draft / Publish flow | Brands edit a draft; publish blocked until required fields are valid |

